text: haey krob rueng teangoasa del yeung nitean brab anak ( mou ham meat) am am pi damnoeng robsa banda anakneasar ku daembi yeung nung pongrung chetd robsa anak tamory vea . haey rueng pit nowknong(chompouk kompir kuor an) nih ban mokadl anak ning chea dambaunman haeyning chea kar kraenromluk muoy samreab anak del mean chomnue teangoasa
